item.title: Irish Webmaster Forum Meetup before BarCamp
item.description: The Irish Webmaster Forum is having a social meetup in Cork the night before BarCamp. If you are local or you are coming down on Friday evening, you’ll be guaranteed an interesting and fun night. All details over on the discussion board.
